# Intito MasterFlow impact analysis for cubes
# Purpose: Evaluate cube dependencies affected by a version diff.
# Sources:
# - IMF.C.Diff
# - Cube definitions that reference the managed dimension
# - IMF.C.Impact
# Parameters:
# - pPrefix: Naming prefix for Intito MasterFlow control objects. Default 'IMF'.
# - pDimensionCode: Managed dimension code.
# - pVersionId: Existing work version.
# Prolog:
# - Resolve diff scope for the selected version.
# Metadata:
# - Identify cubes referencing the managed dimension.
# Data:
# - Evaluate impact severity per affected cube.
# Epilog:
# - Write cube-domain findings to IMF.C.Impact.

sPrefix = Trim(pPrefix);
If(sPrefix @= '');
  sPrefix = 'IMF';
EndIf;

